      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DREAM LINKIN (1) scored two back then drifted back and missed the frame latest finishing a 1.5 lengths 4th at this track (20.19). Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. HEY MARTY (7) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Sizzle Jack (20.04) in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Boasts two wins from four starts out of this box. Expected to be in this for a long way. GINNY RIGGS (3) has mixed form recently, finishing fifth (30.86) in a Grade 5 at Wentworth Park latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Expecting sharp improvement this line-up. MELLCAT BAD BOY (6) is always hard to beat when drawn in this box.",
